  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<h3 id=\"glory-to-mankind\">Glory to Mankind</h3><hr /><p>The YoRHa are a series of advanced androids designed to serve a number of specialized purposes, ranging from combat, to scouting, to healing, and everything in between. They are extremely well practiced in fighting those deemed threats to mankind.</p><h3 id=\"yorha-traits\">YoRHa Traits</h3><hr /><ul><li><strong>Ability Score Increase:</strong> +2 to an ability score, +1 to any other ability score. <em>(Recommended: +2 Dex/Int, +1 Con)</em></li><li><strong>Speed:</strong> Your base walking speed is 35 feet.</li><li><strong>Skill Proficiencies:</strong> You gain 2 skill proficiencies of your choice.</li><li><p><strong>See No Evil:</strong> You gain 60 feet of Blindsight but are blinded, which cannot be removed by means outside of this clan. <br />However, you do not gain disadvantage on Dexterity saving throws, and attacks against you do not gain advantage.</p></li><li><strong>Basic Protocols</strong>: You know 1 additional D-Rank YoRHa Clan Jutsu. This does not count against your jutsu known.</li></ul>",
      "chat": ""
    },
